To install packages:
$ npm install packagename --save-dev
$ bower install packagename --save
  - 1st part of command installs the package code to the project
  - 2nd part of command add package to the manifest file(package.json & bower.json)
    --save-dev adds to the project to the dev dependencies
    --save adds the project to the production dependencies

When cloning, run:
$ npm install
$ bower install
